<h2 class="title"><a href="/articles/string-literals-and-regular-expressions">String literals and regular expressions</a></h2>
<p class="meta"><abbr class="published" title="2006-09-02">2006-09-02</abbr> &bull; <a href="/tag/c++" rel="tag">C++</a>, <a href="/tag/ruby" rel="tag">Ruby</a>, <a href="/tag/puzzles" rel="tag">Puzzles</a>, <a href="/tag/python" rel="tag">Python</a>, <a href="/tag/boost" rel="tag">Boost</a>, <a href="/tag/regex" rel="tag">Regex</a>, <a href="/tag/characters" rel="tag">Characters</a> &bull; <a href="/articles/string-literals-and-regular-expressions#disqus_thread">Comments</a></p>
<div class="toc">
<h2>Contents</h2>
<ul>
 <li><a href="#tocstring-literals" name="toc0" id="toc0">String Literals</a>
 </li>

 <li><a href="#tocescape-sequences" name="toc1" id="toc1">Escape Sequences</a>
 </li>

 <li><a href="#tocliteral-backslashes" name="toc2" id="toc2">Literal Backslashes</a>
 </li>

 <li><a href="#tocregular-expressions" name="toc3" id="toc3">Regular Expressions</a>
 </li>

 <li><a href="#tocattempting-to-match-a-c-string-literal" name="toc4" id="toc4">Attempting to Match a C++ String Literal</a>
 </li>

 <li><a href="#toccorrectly-matching-a-c-string-literal" name="toc5" id="toc5">Correctly Matching a C++ String Literal</a>
 </li>

 <li><a href="#tocnow-lets-do-it-in-c" name="toc6" id="toc6">Now let&#8217;s do it in C++</a>
 </li>

